WEBVTT

00:01.110 --> 00:03.394
- Stay where you are!
- Get down!

00:05.563 --> 00:07.763
A specialist escort
agency for the very rich.

00:07.814 --> 00:09.348
Alex didn't use escorts.

00:09.400 --> 00:12.393
I have to buy a battery for my laptop.

00:12.445 --> 00:15.146
'I stole something... from the attic.'

00:15.197 --> 00:17.439
It's a locked cylinder.

00:17.491 --> 00:21.026
- It needs a code. - Which
you don't know? - No.

00:21.078 --> 00:24.238
I've gone over every
conversation, every word.

00:24.290 --> 00:28.044
Danny, you've got to figure it
out, you're the only one who can.

00:30.004 --> 00:32.705
Did you know that I
suffer from depression?!

00:32.756 --> 00:35.249
Did you know that in the past I drank?!

00:35.301 --> 00:37.584
I didn't know Alex well personally.

00:37.637 --> 00:40.879
There are not many students
who start their degree at 15.

00:40.931 --> 00:42.881
He was murdered.

00:44.060 --> 00:46.468
So I take it you want to
speak to his professor?

00:46.520 --> 00:48.011
Marcus Shore.

00:48.064 --> 00:50.305
Why did they murder him?

00:50.358 --> 00:51.974
I don't know.

00:52.026 --> 00:53.434
Whatever Alex discovered,

00:53.486 --> 00:57.563
whatever it was, whatever it
is, no-one wants in the open.

00:57.615 --> 01:00.274
We're not up against
one intelligence agency,

01:00.326 --> 01:02.901
we're up against them all.

01:03.663 --> 01:05.696
I need information.

01:05.748 --> 01:09.324
What does it mean? It
means we are quite alone.

01:09.377 --> 01:11.326
Get in the car.

01:12.129 --> 01:13.944
It's for you.

01:15.758 --> 01:17.364
Not here!

