01:31.107 --> 01:35.069
'You're looking for answers.

01:37.154 --> 01:39.803
'But are you ready for them?

01:41.784 --> 01:43.869
'Get in the hotel.

01:47.873 --> 01:49.709
'Room 116.'

02:16.319 --> 02:18.195
'The bathroom.

02:28.039 --> 02:29.571
'Get in.

02:29.624 --> 02:31.438
'Clothes on.'

02:51.646 --> 02:53.220
'Now you're clean,

02:53.272 --> 02:55.921
'we can talk a little freer.

02:57.610 --> 02:59.424
'Get changed.

03:08.788 --> 03:10.393
'Outside.'

03:13.250 --> 03:15.409
Where are we going?

03:16.087 --> 03:19.423
'Do you want to know who Alex was or not?'

03:26.222 --> 03:28.172
'The doors are locked, Danny.

03:28.224 --> 03:29.965
'No way out.

03:31.894 --> 03:33.708
'No way back.

03:40.903 --> 03:45.658
'I want to take you on a
journey... into Alex's past.'

03:53.374 --> 03:55.668
'Remember this place?

04:01.882 --> 04:05.052
'Are you sure you know what
really happened in there?

04:10.474 --> 04:12.059
'Walk.'

04:27.158 --> 04:28.691
'A reservation.

04:28.743 --> 04:31.391
'For two.'

04:46.135 --> 04:48.127
There you go.

04:48.179 --> 04:49.503
Menu.

05:24.048 --> 05:25.654
Here I am.

05:29.053 --> 05:30.794
Alex's past.

